{"tid":1597292,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人民日報：《香港人權與民主法案》將嚴重傷害中美關係","createTime":"2019-09-27T01:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T07:52:16.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3354c35d1dcfd4e8cb0d18f9a528db11f1ef0356","tid":1597292,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:26:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1482840_1_20190927082949.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1482840_1_20190927082949.jpg&h=30d38105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》發表文章，指美國國會兩院委員會通過《香港人權與民主法案》，將嚴重傷害中美關係。<br />\n<br />\n文章批評長期以來國內人權領域劣跡斑斑的美國一直秉持雙重標準，大搞干涉別國內政，今次針對中國的香港搞「長臂管轄」，粗暴干涉中國內政，中方強烈譴責、堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n文章指，香港回歸以來，一國兩制、港人治港、高度自治方針得到貫徹落實，香港居民的各項權利和自由依法得到充分保障；香港保持自由港和單獨關稅區地位，保持繁榮穩定符合包括美國在內的各方利益。<br />\n<br />\n文章再次奉勸美方放棄妄想，趕緊收手，停止介入香港事務和粗暴干涉中國內政。美方損害中方利益的任何舉動都將遭到有力回擊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482840-20190927.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482840-20190927.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYrJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=1f312192\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482840-20190927.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b5995339\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482840-20190927.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"070c8e4662a2e4943d9ae02ed13f3daec6e2a594","tid":1597292,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9471ba07c8f5115c9ce376c583a9f86264a40204","tid":1597292,"uid":189404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:32:20.000Z","msg":"越出得多呢d文對我地越有利"},{"pid":"d9ca784f1bf1f91592814bcf7257eda929c5a26a","tid":1597292,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:32:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2ff86e5c43d3f106cfb794301327afbe9ebc6f","tid":1597292,"uid":111576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:33:35.000Z","msg":"回擊未呀？好撚悶呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6632cb3bdbee1e6213278178aee3aea9ba93459d","tid":1597292,"uid":270619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:36:58.000Z","msg":"香港人權與民主法案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80f09e1c62f655db2e6a21cfa60c1b19e93307d","tid":1597292,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:59:15.000Z","msg":"做對了<br />\n<br />\nPush推 <br />\nSignature簽名檔：保衛家園，對抗極權<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>對話係陰險策略：請保持不信任<br />\n不割席、不分化、不篤灰<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做<br />\n誰也不能代表誰、主權在民<br />\n港人治港、高度自治</strong></span><br />\n條例撒回了，但問題根源還在<br />\n反送中運動轉型為「反極權運動」<br />\n守護香港呢個家，尋求深層次改革<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">行動：Connect 新疆/台灣/中共受害者<br />\n大搞文宣，主線：反極權，撐民主自由<br />\n通過人權與民主法案前，減少暴力畫面<br />\n減輕國際戰線壓力，求加辣/高票數通過<br />\n將「自由對抗極權」傳到世界各地</span><br />\n#antitotalitarianism #anti-chinazi <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>麻煩手足暫時停止升級武力(鏡頭前<br />\n文宣/輿論需要時間追上（國際戰線要人<br />\n(抗爭需要轉型,可持續發展)<br />\n要更多機會比和理非參與<br />\n達至全民一齊追求普世價值</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n公平、自由、民主、公義、人權<span style=\"color: gold;\">得來不易</span><br />\n漫長的道路上需要<span style=\"color: gold;\">你支持我，我扶持你</span><br />\n有時惘然若失，但我們也要<span style=\"color: gold;\">自信往前邁步</span><br />\n有咩嘢唔想失去，就努力<span style=\"color: gold;\">捍衛</span>同<span style=\"color: gold;\">守護</span><br />\n現在就用自己雙手實踐夢想，<span style=\"color: gold;\">迎接未來</span><br />\n<br />\n短期目標：改善抗爭能力，提升身份認同<br />\n建議：各有各做，best effort <br />\n中期目標：區議會(94%民主產生)<br />\n建議：關注身邊人，團結一致，各有各做<br />\n長期目標：強化民主陣營勢力<br />\n建議：抗爭生活化，減少比錢極權陣營<br />\n終極目標：民選議會、民選政府<br />\n建議：國際戰線、傳播思想、滲透內部<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公務員</span></strong>：小隱於野，中隱於市，大隱於朝<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和勇合一</strong></span>：1.合法之下，最大勇武<br />\n                     2. 做任何事，永不被捕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">@謠言係疫症&bull;不傳播&bull;去求診&bull;澄清藥<br />\n@FakeNews係Cancer&bull;不擴散&bull;求事實&bull;割<br />\n@接觸資訊時，腦袋要清醒</span><br />\n<br />\n只要爭取民主團火未熄，還是有機會達成<br />\n衛城革命,生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡,打倒腐敗<br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\n<strong><em>升級技能/能力值/level</em></strong>：1. 讀書、識法律2.運動、鬥長命3.和勇合一精神4.批判性思考5.精通專業技能6.低消費、高儲蓄<br />\n<strong><em>每日任務：</em></strong>1.幫襯良心商店、抵制送中商戶2.開AC玩國際戰線 (Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit)3.多發佈正面資訊、冷處理負面POST4.十點咆哮發泄5.思考完就take action<br />\n<strong><em>每星期任務</em></strong>：1. 罷買日2. 教育家中兩老3. 去連儂牆幫手4.參加一樣民主活動5. 諗下點樣爭取民主<br />\n<strong><em>每月任務</em></strong>：1. 換美金，走資2. 陪審員/派傳單/放映會/各有各做<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持；Best effort，你呢？民主尚未成功，同志仍需努力<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYrJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=87c66e61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n理非可以做的事<a href=\"https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTakeActionWithYou&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYrJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=d1abb67b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou</a><br />\n良心與無良商戶<a href=\"https://www.wordsofmouth.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordsofmouth.net%2F&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYrJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=ff99c7de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wordsofmouth.net/</a><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\nVersion 2019.09.27<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">要記住極權如何打壓香港示威：</span></strong><br />\n1.抹黑：利用少部分的暴力衝突而將全部示威者形容為「邪惡」、示威=港獨<br />\n2.誤導：送中條例、說謊、黃色object等等<br />\n3.滲透：5毛、陳雲、黃x民、譚香文<br />\n4.假民意/曲解民意：主流民意是......<br />\n5.5毛輿論-分化、負面、fake news、煽動手足做負效益/低效益工作<br />\n6.強迫企業自我審查<br />\n7.出動黑社會、愛國暴徒<br />\n8.扮示威者：(負面的)破壞eg.遊行<br />\n9.嫁禍示威者：打議員打記者打女仔<br />\n10.扮好人/扮對話：「江山易改本性難移」<br />\n諗到再加</span>"},{"pid":"755513bedb99a6b6774c22ef252dba6c4c6bfa58","tid":1597292,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:00:19.000Z","msg":"又做對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f8fa02d5e0642fcd091539faaebc27be357883","tid":1597292,"uid":22590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:00:30.000Z","msg":"口交部文章產生器"},{"pid":"30c124d17fdb24fead2a4f81f2e3b2cc6f231060","tid":1597292,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:00:51.000Z","msg":"咁撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c311fad4a16eab43fc1aa20323360d700c699e41","tid":1597292,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:01:51.000Z","msg":"自己又粗暴干涉美國內政 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6675ba3ee921e2bde8fe40a49dac825339b0699","tid":1597292,"uid":268026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:02:07.000Z","msg":"唔通貿易戰又唔嚴重傷害？"},{"pid":"5ef19956945c4f0d38d59b0bf776b206f4e03359","tid":1597292,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:02:41.000Z","msg":"支共學人講人權"},{"pid":"8f0bf43bf8343c357330f1f3b6039e535cef0675","tid":1597292,"uid":23764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:03:03.000Z","msg":"邊個想同你中國建立良好關係啊，死撚開啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"de290eb7a74f117f6b424f7dc93fd2eb0fd25445","tid":1597292,"uid":264104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:03:33.000Z","m